<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>game</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
	<%= csp_meta_tag %>
	<%= stylesheet_link_tag 'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
	<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
	
	<%= javascript_pack_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
	<script src="http://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/underscore.js/1.3.3/underscore-min.js"></script>
    <script src="http://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/backbone.js/0.9.2/backbone-min.js"></script>
    <script src="http://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/backbone-localstorage.js/1.0/backbone.localStorage-min.js"></script>
	<%= javascript_pack_tag 'info_table', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
  </head>

  <body>
	<% if user_signed_in? && !current_user.otp_required %>
		<%= render "layouts/header" %>
	<%end%>
	<%= render 'layouts/flashes' %>
	<main>
	<%= yield %>
	<div class="info-window">
                <h3 class="info-window-title">
                    info table
                </h3>
				<%= link_to "X", '#', class: "info-window-close", :"data-turbolinks" => false %>
                <nav class="info-window-nav">
                    <ul class="info-window-nav-list">
                        <li class="info-window-nav-item">
							<%= link_to "site", '#help_site', class: "info-window-nav-item-link", :"data-turbolinks" => false %>
                        </li>
                        <li class="info-window-nav-item">
							<%= link_to "game", '#help_game', class: "info-window-nav-item-link", :"data-turbolinks" => false %>
                        </li>
                        <li class="info-window-nav-item">
							<%= link_to "guilds", '#help_guilds', class: "info-window-nav-item-link", :"data-turbolinks" => false %>
						</li>
                        <li class="info-window-nav-item">
							<%= link_to "tournament", '#help_tournament', class: "info-window-nav-item-link", :"data-turbolinks" => false %>
						</li>
                    </ul>
                </nav>
                <div class="info-window-nav-item-info" id="info-window-nav-item-site">
                    <div class="item-site-block">
                        <img src="assets/images/sword.png" alt="sword" class="item-site-block-icon">
                        <span class="item-site-block-description">- score</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item-site-block">
                        <img src="assets/images/sword.png" alt="sword" class="item-site-block-icon">
                        <span class="item-site-block-description">- users</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item-site-block">
                        <img src="assets/images/sword.png" alt="sword" class="item-site-block-icon">
                        <span class="item-site-block-description">- rank</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item-site-block">
                        <img src="assets/images/sword.png" alt="sword" class="item-site-block-icon">
                        <span class="item-site-block-description">- accept</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="item-site-block">
                        <img src="assets/images/sword.png" alt="sword" class="item-site-block-icon">
                        <span class="item-site-block-description">- win rate</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item-site-block">
                        <img src="assets/images/sword.png" alt="sword" class="item-site-block-icon">
                        <span class="item-site-block-description">- decline</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item-site-block">
                        <img src="assets/images/sword.png" alt="sword" class="item-site-block-icon">
                        <span class="item-site-block-description">- duel</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item-site-block">
                        <img src="assets/images/sword.png" alt="sword" class="item-site-block-icon">
                        <span class="item-site-block-description">- send message</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-window-nav-item-info" id="info-window-nav-item-game">
                    <div class="item-game-block item-game-rules">
                        <p class="item-game-rules-title">Game rules</p>
                        <p class="item-game-rules-description">
                            Rules are short and very simple. For classic match you will have primitive pong game.
                            For win you have to get 21 score!
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item-game-block item-game-rules">
                        <p class="item-game-rules-title">How to create game?</p>
                        <p class="item-game-rules-description">
                            Find games link on header, then go to new game. You can set password, background image,
                            choose as many bonuses as you want to and e.t.c. Also you are free to create ranked match or classic.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item-game-block item-game-rules">
                        <p class="item-game-rules-title">How to join game?</p>
                        <p class="item-game-rules-description">
                            Find games link on header. Here you can see game rooms, which you can join.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-window-nav-item-info" id="info-window-nav-item-guilds">
                    <div class="item-game-block item-game-rules">
                        <p class="item-game-rules-title">Guilds</p>
                        <p class="item-game-rules-description">
                            You can join or create your own guild. Guilds can have wars between each other and have
                            their own rank system.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item-game-block item-game-rules">
                        <p class="item-game-rules-title">For guild owners</p>
                        <p class="item-game-rules-description">
                            You can set image to guild, choose officers and announce a war to other guilds.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item-game-block item-game-rules">
                        <p class="item-game-rules-title">War time</p>
                        <p class="item-game-rules-description">
                            When the "War time" is active a member can ask to fight randomly anyone from the other guild,
                            if no one of the other guild answer the call after a certain amount of time, the match
                            is automatically won
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-window-nav-item-info" id="info-window-nav-item-tournament">
                    <div class="item-game-block item-game-rules">
                        <p class="item-game-rules-title">Tournament</p>
                        <p class="item-game-rules-description">
                            There are a permanent ladder tournament with a match making system with a ladder
                            system.
                            Users can play on the ladder, with a rating system, or play casually, without it affecting
                            their rating. Rules can be different. You are allowed to register to the tournament in a timeframe
                            before said tournament. After win you will get some prizes.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
	</main>
    <!-- 	<footer>
		<span style="display:block">11001001100101110010011001001100001111001011000011101010110000111011001110110110000111100101101111110100111011011101001110001111000011101000</span>
		<%= link_to "help", '#help', class: "footer-help", :"data-turbolinks" => false %>
	</footer>-->
  </body>

</html>
